# SPA routing: Serve index.html for specific routes only
# Note: Domain redirects (pages.dev -> custom domain) must be configured in Cloudflare Dashboard
# Static assets (images, CSS, JS, fonts) are automatically served by Cloudflare Pages
# For production domain, _routes.json handles the catch-all
# For preview deployments, explicit routes below handle SPA routing
